      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-300 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-6 border border-amber-500/30">Shipping &amp; Logistics</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">FOB vs CIF vs DDP: Which Incoterm for African Commodities?</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A plain-English guide to shipping terms, risk transfer points, and choosing the right Incoterm for your commodity imports.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-brand-300">
        <span>March 23, 2026</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-500"></span>
        <span>10 min read</span>
